Steps for project development

1 Getting queries of mongodb ready
 1.1 Making a database(chosing appropriate fields )
 1.2 Creating queries for fetching data

2 Creating a server 
  2.1 Integrating server with Node Js
  2.2 Routing requests using express

3 Testing
3.1 Applying automation testing using mocha and chai
3.2 Making excel file having all the testcases

4 Creating UI using Angular 6
 4.1 Creating Basic searching (show list of jobs)
 4.2 Decoupling app in various component
 4.3 Integrating Google Map Component with Jobs Portal
 4.4 Uploading resumes(uploading data using angular)
 
